{"tid":831861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]買咗50個唔啱用嘅bearing，可以拎嚟做咩？","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T13:02:40.000Z","uid":64994,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fba355453e081d9a82a6022e0cd0c6311aff40c8","tid":831861,"uid":64994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"本身諗住整啲野，貪得意一買買咗50個，拎返嚟試先知唔啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/182106_cdcfed5e1fb51cffe102fafe9c26c87c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F182106_cdcfed5e1fb51cffe102fafe9c26c87c.png&h=d8f2130c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家有5筒依啲濕鳩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依啲bearing唔似fidget spinner用果啲咁順，而且唔識keep住轉<br />\n<br />\nspec: 6804 bearing  內徑20mm*外徑32mm*厚7mm<br />\n<br />\n有無咩建議？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係簡單嘅野，我可以試吓3d print出嚟"},{"pid":"88756f03f508ba39880efc54a3834c5c324466b5","tid":831861,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"你問下老細肯唔肯換其他野啦？<br />\n你話你買錯左"},{"pid":"a910d53a6bee1b5c7c1f1c3d56c4487b07e4b074","tid":831861,"uid":109690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"啲油脂太杰啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攞柴油洗洗佢再上衣車油應該好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317646daa620ab77be2988c7fee5d94fd83ffdd1","tid":831861,"uid":109690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"不過有得退就拎去退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係工業用嘅bearing多數啲油都係咁杰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a606c9e165